Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------------Staff------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「利落」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.36,0:00:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Necro·Macro」总算又重新启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可等了很长时间呦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前没少受你照顾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.34,0:01:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欠你的如数奉还 也算了结了我一桩心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.13,0:01:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人就是 红衣男
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红衣…男
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.08,0:01:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非 这家伙就是「啄木鸟」?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你是不想等到明天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「罪之枝」 「Crow·乌鸦」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:33.30,Logo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(230,200)}曙光社字幕组\NSGS Fansub
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:38.01,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Strict control of reason and reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:42.34,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Cut myself and scream for their insanity
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:46.79,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Wake up into this nightmare that will never end
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:51.43,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}The main attraction of this twisted master plan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:08.46,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I will be your deadman
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:12.87,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}With nothing but this blood on my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:17.39,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stuck in your Wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:21.82,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I wanna make you bleed just like me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:26.23,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}So make me your deadman
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:30.55,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}With only poison in my veins
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:34.91,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stuck in your Wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:37.22,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stuck in a battle I have to make
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:39.91,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I m gonna make you bleed like me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}前几天的死肉祭还蛮有看头的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:48.09,Float,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(595,650)}Carnival Corpse
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的赌注不小心下多了 紧张了一把呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是呢 明天 期待已久的新人终于要登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.41,0:03:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人「啄木鸟」将会与「乌鸦」进行对战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可值得期待啊 我老婆可是「乌鸦」的粉丝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请贵夫妇务必一同欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个「啄木鸟」 是个怎样的「Deadman」呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊 您还是亲自欣赏比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会故弄玄虚啊 又是老一套吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是搞不过你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我先告辞一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉打扰您会客
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有情况发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G栋的旧避难所前「乌鸦」正在发飙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像 在切披萨一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 就是那时的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就如你所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我们稍微为明天来个热身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「啄木鸟」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你愿意 认真地打一场也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说与在中庭时的打扮不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你一言不发傻站在那干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 别让我Orz好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那个「啄木鸟」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啄木……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把全班同学都杀掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长野的（哔哔=疯子）初中生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算把「罪之枝」留到何时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都出了这么多血了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血? 这样说的话 刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 是血
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那股力量是需要血的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 我白期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我失望也要有个限度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无趣的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要为我的朋友 山炸排和美美报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红衣男
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那究竟是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 为什么会无效啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你「利落」地正中了我的心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么仇啊 红衣男啊 我都不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你挺能打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦? 不知道是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 他不是红衣男
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 我哪里红啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那个力量 在学校把我的朋友们都…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了你朋友的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在乱七八糟说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我 我没有杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我才以为你是当时的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是「乌鸦」 千地清正
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不知道你把我和谁搞混了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「罪之枝」的话 你不也能用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 莫非
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为只有你和那个红衣男是「Deadman」?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Deadman」…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在「死囚乐园」的最中央
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个G栋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为关得都是些神马家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你什么也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会以为只有自己才是特殊的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有坏掉的大人和小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对 你就是小鬼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:10:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 来陪我「利落」地玩玩吧 「啄木鸟」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许欺负丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女 女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 许 欺 负 丸 太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.69,0:10:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我知道啦 穿上这个 你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身紧身衣不太好吧 各种不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你欺负丸太的话白就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 晃起来了 我说晃起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的不是红衣男吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.19,0:11:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们 别来妨碍我打…架
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白酱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G栋门前清理完毕 全员捕获
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 那个9061号 让他走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎你那边不太好处理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个…别乱动…行了…跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 创办人 有一个人没有识别代码
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 管理服务器出错了么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒔名长官 又要生气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 不仅是「Necro·Macro」的残骸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连犯人的脚印和指纹 都没有找到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那只老狐狸干的么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒔名长官 您要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去见所长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 按照规定 您必须要取得创始人的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论受到处分还是被解雇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.79,0:12:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不找他直接面谈的话 我是不会罢休的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.69,0:12:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是因为规定 而是为了纪律
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 丸太在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:12:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了正带你过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不准再乱来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监视那帮人就够受的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 为什么要隐藏G栋的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是当然的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那群家伙很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里的所有人 可都是「罪之枝」的发病者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.78,0:13:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪的…发病…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是疾病什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.89,0:13:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道 具体情况我们也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Deadman」 血之能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个监狱到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 丸太呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对外面说这里的事也是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我就当做劳务费收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 我的CP!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这啥呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 放开我 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是收监体检 别乱动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.43,0:14:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十岚丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 都怪你在正式对决前偷打
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 脸好红啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少管我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是发烧了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是麻醉还没过去而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你丫给我换衣服去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 医生穿白衣有什么不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有点抗性好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 白衣服很不妙好不好 各种的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸骨和肋骨有两根 彻底断了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然「利落」地断了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:16:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样子 明天做不了「实验」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我托创办人取消或者换个时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨头折了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会折
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千地清正的干架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别插手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指派律师?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我还有那个身份呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老本行是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个「死囚乐园」的创办人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.57,0:16:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 想把能力者都聚集到此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是需要各种花招的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什么也是常有的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫁祸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我这儿有个特别擅长干那个的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就搞了这么一出呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须得万无一失才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是什么大问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫的 鬼话连篇 死四眼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快解开 草泥马快把这解开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这屎蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草泥马 我绝对不会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须宰了你!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哦 太得寸进尺的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.14,0:17:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没学过敬语么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要学会「您」 「请」 「劳驾」之类的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:43.61,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此处的敬语因为并无实际意义，因此翻成了汉语中常见的敬语
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「您」 「请」 「劳驾」!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉木创办人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负荷太大 会影响明天的「实验」的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你在意了吗 「实验」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天你可要登台呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代号 「啄木鸟」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是你 五十岚丸太 以及
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「乌鸦」 千地清正
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「罪之枝」的发病者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦不 是能力者之间的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「实验」在G栋可是日常行为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.91,0:18:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了的话能取得和之前的Dog Race
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法比拟的CastPoint
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和「Candy」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么能对你唯命是从
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外 要是你能一直取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定还能与你思念之人重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念之人?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 长野事件中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.84,0:19:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全班都惨遭杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.65,0:19:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 准确来说并不是全班
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的 五十岚丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是唯一被留下活口的人这一事实
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只疯狂的怪物 似乎很欣赏你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是你说的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红衣男
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.11,0:19:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「罪之枝」能力的感染源
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是死囚乐园中最恶劣的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:39.37,Float,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(644,648)}Wretched Egg
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原罪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 是在这里么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个红衣男
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.23,0:19:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我见他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.69,0:19:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对要把他和你都宰掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就先登上明天的「实验」——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:19:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死肉祭的舞台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:19:59.58,Float,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(557,650)}Carnival Corpse
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死肉祭 ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:02.91,Float,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(623,650)}Carnival Corpus
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会好玩到爆的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死肉祭——Carnival Corpus
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.68,0:20:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是「死囚乐园」最盛大的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Deadman」——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.06,0:20:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前的「Red Hole」发生之后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.00,0:20:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所出现的「罪之枝」感染者们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了让他们的病症
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是能将那特殊能力充分发挥而设的实验
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.41,0:20:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要内容是 「Deadman」之间的互相残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空前绝后 举世无双的娱乐活动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将要就此展开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂了么 新人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.58,0:21:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们再来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.21,0:21:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要! 不要啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.29,0:22:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个月的「达人」到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.11,0:22:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放那儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.02,0:22:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小鬼 是侥幸还是确有实力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待着呢 「啄木鸟」
